body:
I believe removing the leading slash [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tensorboard/components/tf_backend/router.ts#L39) would fix it?


Do you want to submit a pull request?

n.b. currently Bazel doesn't compile TensorBoard. We're actively fixing this right now. But until the next release, you will need to [recompile the TensorBoard frontend yourself](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tensorboard/DEVELOPMENT.md) to test the fix.
